.PP
Install the \s-1SYSLINUX\s0 bootloader on the device mounted at \f(CW\*(C`directory\*(C'\fR.
Unlike \*(L"syslinux\*(R" which requires a \s-1FAT\s0 filesystem, this can be used on an
